OL,3,C'World's oldest calendar' found carved
OL,4,Conto ancient monument
OL,6,FThe markings also appear to show both
OL,7,Fsolar and lunar cycles, combining the
OL,8,Fmotions of the sun and moon, which the
OL,9,Fresearchers said could represent the
OL,10,Fworld's earliest calendar.
OL,12,FThis calendar also shows 12 lunar
OL,13,Fmonths with 11 additional days, the
OL,14,Fresearchers said. The markings also
OL,15,Fdepict the summer solstice as a
OL,16,Fseparate, special day, represented by
OL,17,Fa "V" worn around the neck of a bird-
OL,18,Flike beast.
