OL,3,C'World's oldest calendar' found carved
OL,4,Conto ancient monument
OL,6,FThis event is thought to have shaped
OL,7,Fhuman civilisation with new
OL,8,Fdevelopments in agriculture and
OL,9,Freligion.
OL,11,FDr Martin Sweatman, of the University
OL,12,Fof Edinburgh's School of Engineering,
OL,13,Fwho led the research, said: "It
OL,14,Fappears the inhabitants of Gobekli
OL,15,FTepe were keen observers of the sky,
OL,16,Fwhich is to be expected given their
OL,17,Fworld had been devastated by a comet
OL,18,Fstrike.
