OL,6,F"This event might have triggered
OL,7,Fcivilisation by initiating a new
OL,8,Freligion and by motivating
OL,9,Fdevelopments in agriculture to cope
OL,10,Fwith the cold climate.
OL,12,F"Possibly, their attempts to record
OL,13,Fwhat they saw are the first steps
OL,14,Ftowards the development of writing
OL,15,Fmillennia later."
